<b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b "> 470010: The paint pulse for NFD could not be (re)calibrated</b> </title><abstract class="- topic/abstract " id="GUID-FCBB817E-8FF6-424C-B2E0-55D8A9CED673"><p class="- topic/p ">Too many nozzles failed on the mentioned printhead to be able to calculate the correct paint characteristics during re-calibration. 
</p><p class="- topic/p "><b class="+ topic/ph hi-d/b ">No actions are required unless the print quality is out of specification.</b>
</p></abstract><prolog class="- topic/prolog "><metadata class="- topic/metadata "><category class="- topic/category ">Diagnostics</category></metadata></prolog><taskbody class="- topic/body task/taskbody "><section id="GUID-527C28C5-1E1A-4103-BC43-BE05BD9E7F6A" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Collect</title><p class="- topic/p "><u class="+ topic/ph hi-d/u ">Calibration step</u>
</p><p class="- topic/p ">This warning is generated during the calibration step: “PrintheadPAINtReference” which is part of the printhead calibration sequence.
</p><p class="- topic/p "><u class="+ topic/ph hi-d/u ">Patterns in calibration print</u>
</p><table id="GUID-40354EB1-BF65-479F-A61F-919DE77EC76C" class="- topic/table "><tgroup cols="2" class="- topic/tgroup "><colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" colwidth="1.00*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col2" colnum="2" colwidth="6.81*" class="- topic/colspec "/><tbody class="- topic/tbody "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">C1640/C1650
</p><p class="- topic/p ">C1630/CMxx
</p></entry><entry colname="col2" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">
</p><fig id="GUID-320D3F00-72D1-4ED3-9094-CC9B05781F94" class="- topic/fig "><image href="GUID-766632B4-099D-40DC-AFE2-89499C3AB1DA-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-766632B4-099D-40DC-AFE2-89499C3AB1DA-low.png"/></fig></entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></section><section id="GUID-563DD250-A861-48A0-90E7-5EA792700CC1" class="- topic/section "><title class="- topic/title ">Analyse/Repair</title><fig id="GUID-A3A2F02A-6C02-4FAB-BEFB-7AA27B00666E" class="- topic/fig "><title class="- topic/title "/><image href="GUID-DE7E9451-9CF3-45CE-91E5-3721AFF183B7-low.png" placement="inline" class="- topic/image " otherprops="GUID-DE7E9451-9CF3-45CE-91E5-3721AFF183B7-svg.svg"/></fig><table id="GUID-83A38745-6813-428B-8495-6FE6CC8E8D5D" class="- topic/table "><tgroup cols="4" class="- topic/tgroup "><colspec colname="col1" colnum="1" colwidth="1.00*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col2" colnum="2" colwidth="1.04*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col3" colnum="3" colwidth="8.36*" class="- topic/colspec "/><colspec colname="col4" colnum="4" colwidth="3.49*" class="- topic/colspec "/><thead class="- topic/thead "><row class="- topic/row "><entry colname="col1" valign="top" class="- topic/entry "><p class="- topic/p ">Step
